{"tid":2260821,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搵到個流浪漢竇 可以點幫佢地","createTime":"2020-10-28T01:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T03:41:48.000Z","uid":86199,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9eafb3f0fdbeeef68e18a8cd8eb7da2598f58a","tid":2260821,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:07:06.000Z","msg":"佢地訓係橋底 就黎冬天 想幫佢地有個家 佢地好凍下 <br />\n<br />\n救幫手 估算有六 七個聚居<br />\n<br />\n見到有人派飯盒<br />\n<br />\n但係唔夠佢地食 好瘦好餓<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lfcrz5i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfcrz5i.jpg&h=230fa911&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b35707f2147418fa8a81f3f6b95a2cb8508ada9","tid":2260821,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:09:45.000Z","msg":"1823"},{"pid":"e1eaf168b22f0595b8396676217277a01cc23e6f","tid":2260821,"uid":27993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:09:58.000Z","msg":"唔知你曲定直<br />\n你唔放張相出黎已經幫左佢地<br />\n如果依個po多人睇既話應該幾日後又有賣港狗去開喉洗地"},{"pid":"149e71e1539a74e2052d8a2ab983d0a81ed54a99","tid":2260821,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e1eaf168b22f0595b8396676217277a01cc23e6f","tid":2260821,"uid":27993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:09:58.000Z","msg":"唔知你曲定直<br />\n你唔放張相出黎已經幫左佢地<br />\n如果依個po多人睇既話應該幾日後又有賣港狗去開喉洗地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:11:19.000Z","msg":"雖然我對依張圖入面個流浪漢好反感<br />\n霸撚哂D野 咁多野周圍放"},{"pid":"895eee2e13121bcde0a57189e3c77a001c5a4b6f","tid":2260821,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:12:23.000Z","msg":"關你撚事"},{"pid":"b420ef675dc098238821b9efe596051b6a186677","tid":2260821,"uid":373455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:17:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"688a7915e9b82d132a897217de890746a03b6f01","tid":2260821,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:17:38.000Z","msg":"之前識個老人家有公屋<br />\n但係每日執垃圾放屋企<br />\n放到間屋冇位入自己就落樓下天橋訓<br />\n<br />\n過左一段時間，有人投訢佢間屋出現惡臭同多甲由<br />\n<br />\n我去左做義工幫佢執屋，淨係垃圾都清左超過廿袋，間屋淨係單車都放左十幾廿部<br />\n<br />\n後來聽聞佢番屋住多幾日都係執野執到搬番天橋住"},{"pid":"efba879c4789aaefee5aa37be4dd798041bf0c81","tid":2260821,"uid":380193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:21:51.000Z","msg":"直接派錢"},{"pid":"ddfa3db5a969d76bccacc12f8a97a6b71761cbc8","tid":2260821,"uid":217092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:30:32.000Z","msg":"老實講 無咩可以做到<br />\n有啲case係搞咗好耐安排間屋比佢地住<br />\n但最尾佢地都係中意瞓翻公園多啲"},{"pid":"d583d2208457606332c234e83265674af2572878","tid":2260821,"uid":5178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2260588/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2260588/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7e33223691add4169690a6eb715e6f42e7989d5c","tid":2260821,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:39:36.000Z","msg":"叫佢地去晒你屋企訓"},{"pid":"331969036dcc23df455f8a8667508f1d4f0fa118","tid":2260821,"uid":121185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:41:48.000Z","msg":"有能力的話收養佢地"}]}